reviewText: Love this movie, though it ought to be a digital download. The tape I had messed up. Wish I could buy this as an instant video. It is like only selling music on 8 track.
vhs tape tracking is poor will not play clearly
I loved this movie and I really wish it would come out on DVD. Jonathan Silverman is great. So is his roomate George Newbern. Great college movie. Alyssa Milano is hot...Maybe one day!
I bought this VHS tape so I can copy it over to a DVD. The quality isn't so great... kinda grainy like you would expect from a VHS tape, but it's better than nothing.

I liked this one, because it made you try to understand from a different perspective point. You know, walk a mile in someone else's shoes for a while thing! Plus, Alyssa Milano had just finished wrapping up with her TV show "Who's The Boss?" during or about that year.

This is a little known movie of Alyssa Milano's but I

like this movie a lot.  Alyssa in her younger days.  Not on DVD.

I'm a buyer of it if it was.  If you are a Alyssa fan, you

want this movie.
